    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce a new rule for MPs to take an oath to adhere to the Nolan principles",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "We think that all MPs should adhere to the Nolan principles. At the moment, we do not think that they follow them. We want all MPs to take an oath to follow the Nolan principles, and be scrutinised if they fail. We feel that there is a lack of public accountability at the moment.",
